---
title: Ultimate Grilled Chicken Burger Sandwich with  Mango Salad
description: Bring on the long weekend with a show-stopping, mouth-watering brie-topped chicken burger. And don't overlook the juicy mango salad. It's bound to become a part of your summer repertoire!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ultimate-grilled-chicken-burger-sandwich-c31236c0.jpg
